     "750 ml kaas<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broccoli-hoender-blog-025.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broccoli-hoender-blog-025-1024x768.jpg\" title=\"Broccolihoender - my kinders se gunsteling\" alt=\"broccoli hoender blog 025\" class=\"direction-step-image\" loading=\"lazy\"></a>"
