  "directionsTitle": "Metode",
  "directionGroups": [
   {
    "title": null,
    "steps": [
     "Sny jou ui in ringe en braai in n bietjie olie tot deurskynend in &#8216;n pot op die stoof.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broccoli-hoender-blog-002.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broccoli-hoender-blog-002.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"broccoli hoender blog 002\" title=\"Broccolihoender - my kinders se gunsteling\"></a>",
     "Braai nou jou hoender saam met jou uie tot bruin.",
     "Gooi die wyn, water, naeltjies, roosmaryn en tiemie by die hoender.  Kook die hoender tot sag.( plus minus 40 minute).<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broccoli-hoender-blog-017.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broccoli-hoender-blog-017.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"broccoli hoender blog 017\" title=\"Broccolihoender - my kinders se gunsteling\"></a>",
     "Haal die hoender uit en pluis dit in n oondbak &#8211; moenie die sous weggooi waarin jy die hoender gekook het nie.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broccoli-hoender-blog-031.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broccoli-hoender-blog-031.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"broccoli hoender blog 031\" title=\"Broccolihoender - my kinders se gunsteling\"></a>",
     "Sout en peper die fyn hoender.<br>",
     "Spoel die broccoli af onder lopende water.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broccoli-hoender-blog-019.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broccoli-hoender-blog-019.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"broccoli hoender blog 019\" title=\"Broccolihoender - my kinders se gunsteling\"></a>",
     "Kook nou die broccoli tot net sag in die sous waarin jy die hoender gekook het.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broccoli-hoender-blog-029.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broccoli-hoender-blog-029.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"broccoli hoender blog 029\" title=\"Broccolihoender - my kinders se gunsteling\"></a>",
     "Dreineer en sit die broccoli op die hoender.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broccoli-hoender-blog-046.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broccoli-hoender-blog-046.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"broccoli hoender blog 046\" title=\"Broccolihoender - my kinders se gunsteling\"></a>",
     "In &#8216;n pot op die stoof meng die melk en die sampioensoppoeier en laat dit 3 minute saggies prut.",
     "Gooi die mayonnaise, die kerrie en die suurlemoensap by die sampioensopmengsel &#8211; roer met n draadklitser dat daar nie klontjies in is nie.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broccoli-hoender-blog-039.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broccoli-hoender-blog-039.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"broccoli hoender blog 039\" title=\"Broccolihoender - my kinders se gunsteling\"></a>",
     "Laat dit prut vir 5 minute en gooi dit oor die hoender en broccoli in die oondbak.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broccoli-hoender-blog-050.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broccoli-hoender-blog-050.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"broccoli hoender blog 050\" title=\"Broccolihoender - my kinders se gunsteling\"></a>",
     "Strooi die kaas oor.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broccoli-hoender-blog-054.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broccoli-hoender-blog-054.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"broccoli hoender blog 054\" title=\"Broccolihoender - my kinders se gunsteling\"></a>",
     "Bak dit vir 40 minute by 180 grade celsius.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broccoli-hoender-blog-110.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broccoli-hoender-blog-110.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"broccoli hoender blog 110\" title=\"Broccolihoender - my kinders se gunsteling\"></a>"
    ]
